<p>The couple announced the birth of their baby girl on August 10, taking to Instagram to share a sweet photo of the parents holding their newborn's tiny hand.</p>

<p>'We are beyond thrilled to announce the birth of our daughter, Lyla Maria Schwarzenegger Pratt,' Pratt said. 'We couldn’t be happier.'</p>

<p>'Both mom and baby are doing great. We are extremely blessed,' he continued, signing off: 'Love Katherine and Chris.'</p>

